            <div src="" class="col-md-2">
              <%= image_tag("placeholder.png", size: '100x100') %>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body-text col-md-10">
              <div>
                Spend a morning at a farmers' market. These markets don't have to be a simply a food
                shopping trip. Take the time to speak to the farmers who grow the produce that you eat.
                Try the different samples available. Bring friends and family with you on this trip.
                These markets are special and differ from typical grocery stores in that they're community
                events. It's an opportunity to connect with the people who grow the food you eat and learn
                about how and where your food is grown.
              </div>

