                while reducing your ecological footprint. And not to mention, making these choices are better
                for your health. Unprocessed foods are nutrient dense and filled with vitamins and minerals
                that your body needs. Buy a week's worth of groceries, but cost break it down so you know
                how much the meal you make cost.
